General setup
- license pycharm
- install IdeaVim plugin
- set IDE font to 14.0
- Add black as external tool - https://black.readthedocs.io/en/stable/integrations/editors.html
- Add ruff as external tool - https://beta.ruff.rs/docs/editor-integrations/#pycharm-external-tool
- set python interpreter to use poetry's current setup
- allow for repeated keys
defaults write com.jetbrains.pycharm ApplePressAndHoldEnabled -bool false
defaults read com.jetbrains.pycharm ApplePressAndHoldEnabled
